<template>
    <!-- Sheet Modal -->
        <ion-content>
            <ion-card class="card">
                <ion-card-header>
                <ion-card-title v-for="item in spot" :key="item.name">
                {{ item.name }}
                </ion-card-title>
                </ion-card-header>
                <ion-card-content v-for="item in spot" :key="item.name">
                    {{ item.description }}
                    <ion-button 
                        expand="block" 
                        @click="presentActionSheet">
                        Block Button
                    </ion-button>
                </ion-card-content>
            </ion-card>
        </ion-content>
</template>

<script>
import { defineComponent } from 'vue';
import { useCounterStore } from '@/stores/counter'
import { supabase } from "@/supabase"
import { IonContent } from '@ionic/vue';
import { IonCard, IonCardContent, IonCardHeader, IonCardTitle, IonButton, actionSheetController } from '@ionic/vue';

export default defineComponent({
  name: 'Tab2Page',
  components: {
    IonContent,
    IonCard, 
    IonCardContent, 
    IonCardHeader, 
    IonCardTitle,
    IonButton
    },
  data: () => ({
    spot: '',
    markers: [],
  }),
  setup() {
  },
  async created() {
    const counter = useCounterStore()
    console.log(counter.count)
    const {data: events} = await supabase
      .from('events')
      .select('description,name')
      .eq('id', counter.count)
    console.log(events)
    this.spot = events
  },
  methods: {
  }
});
</script>

<style scoped>
.card {
    margin-top: 15px;
}
</style>
